,"tid":239181,"uid":1018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=26610081\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.discuss.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Faction%3Dthread%26tid%3D26610081&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=10a7bc82\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=26610081</a><br />\n<br />\n個條小斯以為 air India 係廉航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實小斯係男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9acb6f25589ec51e631495d0874b77d3ef6d0f","tid":239181,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:51:05.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d88002f539b44975618273b99c7b2aa92eaa157","tid":239181,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:53:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=26610081\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.discuss.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Faction%3Dthread%26tid%3D26610081&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=10a7bc82\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=26610081</a><br />\n<br />\n個條小斯以為 air India 係廉航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實小斯係男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人妖"},{"pid":"a0df87f499d742bfd5e7083d4ebfa2f3362d03d3","tid":239181,"uid":34029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:54:33.000Z","msg":"遲到 比你上係人情 唔比上係自己抵撚死 <br />\n試過遲大到最後比上"},{"pid":"96dac83a4fc125d873f48c4b078719a1dce68b36","tid":239181,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲到 比你上係人情 唔比上係自己抵撚死 <br />\n試過遲大到最後比上</blockquote><br />\n所以 check-in 同 boarding 都係準時到"},{"pid":"d33c72808de71ee20693288e666513c9a22a2c71","tid":239181,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>遲到 比你上係人情 唔比上係自己抵撚死 <br />\n試過遲大到最後比上</blockquote><br />\n所以 check-in 同 boarding 都係準時到</blockquote><br />\n比人搬埋行理落黎都幾誇張.會唔會final call左佢好耐?<br />\nboarding time同起飛時間唔同,睇佢寫起飛時間前7分鐘.應該過左好耐"},{"pid":"ed387bbf7640b7b1b8d14e422edfbb42b58e8dbb","tid":239181,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:30:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>遲到 比你上係人情 唔比上係自己抵撚死 <br />\n試過遲大到最後比上</blockquote><br />\n所以 check-in 同 boarding 都係準時到</blockquote><br />\n比人搬埋行理落黎都幾誇張.會唔會final call左佢好耐?<br />\nboarding time同起飛時間唔同,睇佢寫起飛時間前7分鐘.應該過左好耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果真係機等人果隻，真係早半個鐘前已經開始上機<br />\n<br />\n試過有次等上機等到瞓着咗，1:50班機，1:25已經全機上晒，有職員過嚟叫醒我，問我係咪去邊度，我先知道全部人無晒。<br />\n<br />\n再瞓就 MISS 班機，等OFFLOAD 行李了。"},{"pid":"b56621afab6d6dfbd899ee2e82173307ade406bf","tid":239181,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:51:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>遲到 比你上係人情 唔比上係自己抵撚死 <br />\n試過遲大到最後比上</blockquote><br />\n所以 check-in 同 boarding 都係準時到</blockquote><br />\n比人搬埋行理落黎都幾誇張.會唔會final call左佢好耐?<br />\nboarding time同起飛時間唔同,睇佢寫起飛時間前7分鐘.應該過左好耐</blockquote><br />\n睇上文下理應該係較到最忟個隻<br />\n試過早機因航去台北<br />\n早左兩個鐘到機場<br />\n去到無論係 counter 定 self-drop baggage 都勁多人<br />\n出境又勁多人<br />\n出左境買左個老麥<br />\n再趕到去boarding gate (仲要係60幾號閘）已經boarding緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2712c12fda300fd93eeb4fdb2c9c87d56e8a276","tid":239181,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>遲到 比你上係人情 唔比上係自己抵撚死 <br />\n試過遲大到最後比上</blockquote><br />\n所以 check-in 同 boarding 都係準時到</blockquote><br />\n比人搬埋行理落黎都幾誇張.會唔會final call左佢好耐?<br />\nboarding time同起飛時間唔同,睇佢寫起飛時間前7分鐘.應該過左好耐</blockquote><br />\n睇上文下理應該係較到最忟個隻<br />\n試過早機因航去台北<br />\n早左兩個鐘到機場<br />\n去到無論係 counter 定 self-drop baggage 都勁多人<br />\n出境又勁多人<br />\n出左境買左個老麥<br />\n再趕到去boarding gate (仲要係60幾號閘）已經boarding緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過起台灣離起飛時間45min先到櫃位。結果當然上唔到機<br />\n不過eva 好快幫我安排尾班機(淡季).仲要個地勤好似曾愷玄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事主講個D野好難信係佢一寄左行理就全力衝去gate"}]}